quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,"Ne toto khwalonga Omundu okhurula khwiloba eliumu, elirusinjia- omwoyo- isauti(nilituywa) elirulana nende amatoyi karebwakhwo ifwani"
  15,27,"Ne Amajiini khwakalonga imbeli awo, okhurulana nende omuyeka kwo mulilo"
  15,28,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo olwayaboolela Malaika mbu; “Toto esie nditsa okhulonga Omundu okhurula khuliloba liwumukhanga, lirulana nende amatoyi akarebwamwo ifwani"
  15,29,"Kho olwa ndalamala okhumulonga mana nemufuramwo emiuya chianje, mumwinamile khulwa okhumuwa eshiribwa"
  15,30,Abamalaika boosi halala nibamwinamila
  15,31,"Halali Ibilisi, yakhaya okhuba halala nende balia benama"
  15,32,(Nyasaye)Naboola mbu; “Ewe Ibilisi obele orie olabeele halala nende abenaame?”
  15,33,"Naboola; “Shenyala okhwinamila Omundu wawaloonga khuliloba eliumu lirusinjia -omwoyo- isauti, elirula khu matoyi karebwakhwo ifwani tawe.”"
  15,34,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “ rula omo, oli omutsube’’"
  15,35,Ne toto oli nende eshilamo shianje okhula inyanga yeyindukho.”
  15,36,Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi! Mbelesie obwiyangu okhula inyanga yabalilamusibwa”
  15,37,(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “toto ewe olimubalia bahebwa obwiyangu
  15,38,Okhula inyanga yebise bimanyishe biarebwaho .”
  15,39,Naboola;“Nyasayewanje!shingalawambusilia okhukora nditsa okhubaronela(abandu) khushialo ne nditsa okhubakosia boosi.”
  15,40,Halali Abasumba bobo abatswenufu”
  15,41,(Nyasaye) naboola mbu “ino ni injila yokhwitsa ewanje ingololofu”
  15,42,"“Ne toto Abandu banje ewe sholaba nende obunyali khubo tawe, halali balia abakori bakhulondakhwo"
  15,43,"Ne toto Jahannam niho habundu wabu, wabakasilibwa bosi"
  15,44,"Ili nende emiliango saba, nebuli omuliango kuli nende ebuleka yakabulwa"